Fortean Times - March 2015
 English | 84 pages | True PDF | 17.00 Mb


Fortean Times is a British monthly magazine devoted to the anomalous phenomena popularised by Charles Fort. Previously published by John Brown Publishing (from 1991 to 2001) and then I Feel Good Publishing (2001 to 2005), it is now published by Dennis Publishing Ltd. As of December 2014, its circulation was just under 14,300 copies per month.[2] The magazine's tagline is "The World of Strange Phenomena
